div.div: make some minor updates to documentation
add section documenting how to access log files and listing all available commands and options
add output of ls -l for python generated script to show the full path prior to viewing content.
update example output for pbs examples

update documentation for buildtest features to document removing executors. Make a few changes to shell page by showing output of test dynamically using 'buildtest path' command. There was an issue with retrieving correct report file when using 'buildtest path'. It was retrieving the default report file and not honoring the option 'buildtest --report' if specified to specify an alternate report file
